transactioncolumncustomfield.description: A checkbox to indicate that the quantity on this sales order line does not represent hours even though we are creating a time billing rule in SuiteProjects Pro. When checked, the quantity on invoice line items referencing this line from the sales order will be recalculated to % invoiced for that line when the invoice is exported.
